    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 4 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 17 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 5 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 17</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>In order to use this technique, you must be grappling with the target, the target must be within 1 size category of you, and neither of you can be prone or pinned. Both you and the target twist several times in midair, both falling prone. As a result, the target will be pinned by you, and suffers 1d4 bludgeoning damage per 5 levels (Reflex halves the damage).</p>\n\n\n\n",
